"""Fake builder for the artifact-binding e2e test (test_artifact_binding.py).

Always writes a CORRECT greet.py (converges in one iteration -- scenario
pass/fail is irrelevant to what this fixture is proving) PLUS a symlink
planted directly in the workspace root. Every dev/final scenario passes
(the symlink is never exercised by any scenario command), but the
converged workspace is hostile content df_seal.freeze() must refuse
